            <li><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf-fill pdf-icon"></i><span class="pdf-link">Compendium of OMs and Notifications regarding RTI Act.pdf (2.4 MB)</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf-fill pdf-icon"></i><span class="pdf-link">Annual Report of the Central Information Commission.pdf (3.2 MB)</span></li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf-fill pdf-icon"></i><span class="pdf-link">Standard Operating Procedure for handling RTI applications.pdf (450 KB)</span></li>
